WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.290 --> 00:00:07.609
The world is full of Bible preaching and quoting
hypocrites.

00:00:07.609 --> 00:00:14.790
They preach the Bible, but they do not know
Jesus of the Bible.

00:00:14.790 --> 00:00:18.010
You can see it from their deeds.

00:00:18.010 --> 00:00:22.990
They indulge in the same sins as the world.

00:00:22.990 --> 00:00:33.010
They destroy the world, they wage wars, they
kill other people and yet they evangelize

00:00:33.010 --> 00:00:34.300
the world.

00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:41.800
They send missionaries all over the world
to become just like them, hypocrites, fornicators,

00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:50.120
conformed to the world who even kill, abort,
their own children.

00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:55.079
They are involved in all kinds of sexual immorality.

00:00:55.079 --> 00:01:03.770
