in your heart and you know what is pleasing

00:01:55.250 --> 00:02:02.119
to Him, AND IF YOU LOVE HIM, you DO those
things.

00:02:02.119 --> 00:02:11.260
You turn away from sin, from serving yourself,
from going after the things of the world,

00:02:11.260 --> 00:02:18.810
from hurting and killing other people and
blessing those who go and kill others, and

00:02:18.810 --> 00:02:19.830
you serve Jesus.

00:02:19.830 --> 00:02:21.639
You obey Him.

00:02:21.639 --> 00:02:25.609
You LOVE your neighbor, you don't KILL your
neighbor.

00:02:25.609 --> 00:02:31.969
Dear friends, who are we fooling?

00:02:31.969 --> 00:02:38.349
