00:02:38.349 --> 00:02:45.560
If we are children of God then we will have
the likeness of Jesus Christ.

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:53.370
He came and showed us how a son of God will
behave, how he will live.

00:02:53.370 --> 00:03:02.989
He will live in fellowship with his Father
all the time, doing everything to please God,

00:03:02.989 --> 00:03:09.700
